---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import IndexMobile from '../components/IndexMobile.astro';

---

<Layout title="Welcome to Gazpacho.">
<main class="max-md:hidden">

<div class="containerHeader">
	<div class="intro">
	<h1>Welcome to <span class="text-gradient">Gazpacho</span></h1>
	<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="30" height="50" fill="currentColor" class="svg" viewBox="0 0 16 16">
		<path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M8 1a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v11.793l3.146-3.147a.5.5 0 0 1 .708.708l-4 4a.5.5 0 0 1-.708 0l-4-4a.5.5 0 0 1 .708-.708L7.5 13.293V1.5A.5.5 0 0 1 8 1"/>
	  </svg></div>

</div>
<div class="containerGrid">

<div class="grid">
<div class="grid-item order">
<p>Commande en ligne</p>
</div>
<div class="grid-item">
<img class="img order" src="order.png" alt="Descripción de la imagen">
</div>
<div class="grid-item menu">
<p>Menu</p>
</div>
<div class="grid-item wide">
<img class="img" src="filetes.jpg" alt="Descripción de la otra imagen">
</div>
<div class="grid-item wide">
<img class="img" src="papas.jpg" alt="Descripción de la tercera imagen">
</div>
<div class="grid-item about wide">
<p>Gazpacho | Qui sommes-nous?</p>
</div>
<div class="grid-item ">
<img class="img2" src="sushi_vaso.jpg" alt="Descripción de la imagen grande">
</div>
<div class="grid-item last-row">
<div class="last-row-container ">
<div class="grid-item last-row">
<img class="img" src="tiramisu.jpg" alt="Descripción de la cuarta imagen">
</div>
<div class="grid-item last-row">
<img class="img" src="mini_hamb.jpg" alt="Descripción de la quinta imagen">
</div>
<div class="grid-item contact last-row">
<p>Contact</p>
</div>
<div class="grid-item last-row">
<img class="img" src="menu_sushi.jpg" alt="Descripción de la sexta imagen">
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="grid-item full-width nous">
<div class="flexContainer">
<h2>A propos</h2>
<div class="line"></div>
<div class="containText">
<p>Gazpacho est un food truck qui prépare des plats internationaux faits maison. Venez découvrir une cuisine savoureuse et authentique, inspirée par des recettes du monde entier, servie avec passion et fraîcheur directement à partir de notre camion.</p>
<a class="link" href="/contact">Contactez-nous</a>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>

</div>
<Footer/>
</main>
<div class="md:hidden">
	<IndexMobile/>
</div>
</Layout>

<style>
	main{
		width: 100%;
	}
h1 {


font-size: 4rem;
font-weight: 700;
line-height: 1;
text-align: center;
margin-bottom: 1em;
color: white;
}
.text-gradient {
background-image: var(--accent-gradient);
-webkit-background-clip: text;
-webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
background-size: 400%;
background-position: 0%;
}
.text{
color: white;
}
.intro{
	position: absolute;
	top: 50%;
	left: 50%;
	transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
	display: flex;
	flex-direction: column;
	justify-content: center;
	align-items: center;
	& .svg{
		fill: whitesmoke;
		transform: scale(2.5);
		animation: move 2s infinite;
}

	}
	@keyframes move {
  0% {
    transform: scale(2.5) translateY(0);
  }
  50% {
    transform: scale(2.5) translateY(10px);
  }
  100% {
    transform: scale(2.5) translateY(0);
  }
}
.containerHeader{
padding: 0;
margin: 0;
width: 100%;
height: 80vh;
position:relative;
background-image: url("foodTruck.jpeg");
background-repeat: no-repeat;
background-position: bottom center;
background-size: cover;
background-attachment: fixed;

}
.containerGrid{
} 
.grid{
display: grid;
grid-template-columns: repeat(5, 1fr);
width: 100%;
}
.grid-item{
position: relative;
place-content: center;
place-items: center;
display: flex;
justify-content: center;
align-items: center;
max-height: 19.5313rem;
}
.img{
width: 100%;
height: 100%;
object-fit: cover;
}
.img2{
width: 100%;
height: 100%;
object-fit: cover;
}
.grid-item.wide {
grid-column: span 2;
}

.grid-item.full-width {
grid-column: span 5;
width: 100%;
height: auto;
min-height: 26rem;
}
.order{
background: #DA780D;
color:antiquewhite;
font-size:2.5rem;
padding: 0 1.1rem;
}
.menu{
background: #1C3B6A;
font-size:2.5rem;
color: antiquewhite;
padding: 0 1.1rem;
}
.about{
background: #ffa545eb;
padding: 0 1.1rem;
font-size:2.5rem;
color :antiquewhite;
}
.contact{
background: #72a1e7;
font-size:2.5rem;
color: antiquewhite;
padding: 0 1.1rem;
}
.nous{
background: rgb(67, 67, 67);
font-size:2.5rem;
padding: 0 1.1rem;
}
.flexContainer{
display: flex;
flex-direction: row;
align-items: flex-start;
justify-content: space-around;
width: 100%;
color: whitesmoke;
padding: 0 15rem;

	& h2{
		flex-grow: 1;
		font-size: 1.8rem

}
}
.line{
width: 10%;
height: 1px;
background: white;
margin: 20px 0;
flex-grow: 1;
}
.containText{
display: flex;
flex-direction: column;
align-items: end;
flex-grow: 1;

	& p{
		text-align: end;
		max-width: 550px;
		font-size: 1.3rem;
	}
	& .link{
		font-size: 1.2rem;
		border: 1px solid white;
		border-radius: 2rem;
		padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
	}
}
.grid-item.last-row {
grid-column: span 5;
width: 100%;
}
.last-row-container {
display: flex;
width: 100%;
}

.grid-item.last-row {
flex-grow: 1;
}
	

</style>
